<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>实力拍</title>
	<meta name="keywords" content="实力拍, 人才拍卖">
	<meta name="description" content="实力拍是深圳市红领巾网络科技有限公司旗下的项目">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0">
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
	<meta name="format-detection" content="email=no">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="../img/logo_ico.ico">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/mobile/global.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/mobile/placebid.css">
	
	<script src="../js/common/zepto.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/mobile/uiservice.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/mobile/placebid.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="viewport">
		<div class="bid-wrap">
			<div class="top-bar">
				<i class="top-bar-spec"><img class="top-bar-ico" src="/img/app_back.png"/></i>
				<span>我要竞拍</span>
				<div class="clear"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="info-status-warp">
				<div class="title">
					<span>请输入初步的薪资条件来邀请他面试</span>
				</div>
				<div class="title">
					<span>初步月薪：</span>
					<input id="minBidPrice" type="text" maxlength="4" onkeyup="value=value.replace(/[^\d.]/g,'')"><span class="price_a">K&nbsp;</span>
					<span>—&nbsp;</span>
					<input id="maxBidPrice" type="text" maxlength="2" onkeyup="value=value.replace(/[^\d]/g,'')"><span class="price_a">K</span>
				</div>
				<div class="title">
					<span>是否提供期权：</span>
					是&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="opt_1 radio disabled"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;否&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="opt_0 radio"></span>
				</div>
				<div class="context">
					<span class="f_b">邀请短笺</span>
					<textarea  id="workTitle" placeholder="例如：希望他担任什么职位（35字内）" maxlength="35"></textarea>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="button">发送面试邀请</div>		
		</div>
		
		<div class="success">
			<div class="tips">
				<span>您的竞价已经提交成功</span>
				<span><i>3</i>秒后自动跳转</span>
				<span>未自动跳转，请<a href="">点击这里</a></span>		
			</div>
		</div>		
	</div>
</body>
</html>
